{"article_id":"OWjzi1qFNDW4Rjyg","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Amid renewed hope Sunday","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that a summit next month between President Trump and North Korean leader Kim Jong-un will actually happen ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"South Korea ' s president said","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"that Mr. Kim committed over the weekend to a denuclearization of the peninsula","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"he wants to work toward peace .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"A U.S. delegation arrived in North Korea on Sunday","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"as preparations for the talks continue .","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"Mr. Trump announced last week","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"he was ending them over North Korean hostilities","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"but now says","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"negotiations have picked back up","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"and he spoke Sunday","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"as if the summit was a \" go . \"","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" Our United States team has arrived in North Korea","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"to make arrangements for the Summit between Kim Jong-un and myself .","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"I truly believe","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"North Korea has brilliant potential","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"and will be a great economic and financial Nation one day .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"Kim Jong-un agrees with me on this .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"It will happen ! \"","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Mr. Trump tweeted Sunday afternoon .","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"U.S. lawmakers said","depth":5},{"id":23,"text":"that","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"while renewed discussions about the Trump-Kim summit are a positive step ,","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"the U.S. can ' t give away too much","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"and should be wary of any supposed commitments","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"coming from Mr. Kim .","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"But South Korean President Moon Jae-in said Sunday","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"that the reclusive North Korean leader is indeed committed to a full denuclearization of the peninsula ,","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"after the two leaders gathered in an impromptu meeting Saturday","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"in hopes","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"of jump-starting diplomatic talks once more .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Mr . Moon told reporters Sunday","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that Mr. Kim at a meeting at the Demilitarized Zone","depth":13},{"id":35,"text":"that separates the two Koreas","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"\" again made clear his commitment to a complete denuclearization of the Korean Peninsula. \"","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"According to Mr . Moon ,","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"the North Korean leader said","depth":12},{"id":39,"text":"he ' s willing to cooperate","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"to end confrontation","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"and work toward peace for the sake of a successful North Korea-U.S. summit .","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"Mr . Moon said","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"he told Mr. Kim in return","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"that Mr. Trump has a \" firm resolve \"","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"to end hostile relations with North Korea","depth":14},{"id":46,"text":"and initiate economic cooperation","depth":14},{"id":47,"text":"if Pyongyang implements \" complete denuclearization . \"","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"According to the State Department ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"the U.S. team met with North Korean officials at the same DMZ site , the village of Panmunjom .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"The U.S. delegation reportedly included Sung Kim , U.S. ambassador to the Philippines and a former U.S. special representative for North Korea policy .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" We ' re looking at June 12 in Singapore .","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"That hasn ' t changed , \"","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"Mr. Trump told reporters earlier the weekend .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Mr. Trump called off the summit Thursday","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"following threats of nuclear war from North Korea ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"only to give fresh hope Friday","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"that negotiations","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"to stage the summit","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"were in the works .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"people want to see","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"if we can get the meeting","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"and get something done , \"","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"\" We get that done","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"and we can be successful in the denuclearization of the Korean peninsula ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"that would be a great thing for North Korea ,","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"it would be a great thing for South Korea ,","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"it would be great for Japan ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"it would be great for the world ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"it would be great for the United States ,","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"it would be great for China . \"","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"But Mr . Moon also made clear","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"that any steps","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"to dial back Mr. Kim ' s nuclear capabilities","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"could come with strings attached .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"\" What Kim is unclear about is that he has concerns","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"about whether his country can surely trust the United States over its promise","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"to end hostile relations","depth":15},{"id":80,"text":"( with North Korea )","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"and provide a security guarantee","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"if they do denuclearization , \"","depth":12},{"id":83,"text":"Mr . Moon said .","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"The North has previously used the term \" denuclearization \"","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"to demand the United States pull out its 28,500 troops in South Korea","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"and withdraw its so-called \" nuclear umbrella \" security commitment to South Korea and Japan .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"The North hasn ' t specified those demands during Mr. Kim ' s sudden outreach to Seoul and Washington in recent months .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Mr . Moon has insisted","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Mr. Kim can be persuaded to abandon his nuclear facilities , materials and bombs in a verifiable and irreversible way in exchange for credible security and economic guarantees .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Mr . Moon said Sunday","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"that the North ' s disarmament could be still be a difficult process","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"even if Pyongyang , Washington and Seoul don ' t differ over what \" complete denuclearization \" of the peninsula means .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"Members of Congress said","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"the devil ,","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"as is always the case with North Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"will be in the details .","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"\" We ' ve got the South Korean president ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"I believe ,","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"providing a great benefit in this discussion ,","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"unless we are not all communicating in the same way , \"","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"said Sen. Roy Blunt , Missouri Republican , on \" Fox News Sunday .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"\" \" You know ,","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"what does denuclearization mean ?","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"What do they expect to see happen ?","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"And I think","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"these talks can produce results .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"But we need results","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"and they need to be very visible","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"before the United States creates any benefits , \"","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":111,"text":"Sen. Marco Rubio , Florida Republican , said","depth":7},{"id":112,"text":"he ' s skeptical","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that Mr. Kim will agree to completely give up his country ' s nuclear capabilities ,","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"the leader has an almost emotional attachment to them","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"and that they make him feel prestigious and powerful .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"\" Ultimately , I remain convinced","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"that he does not want to denuclearize -","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"in fact , he will not denuclearize .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"But he wants to give off this perception","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"that he ' s this open leader ,","depth":13},{"id":122,"text":"that he ' s peaceful ,","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"that he ' s reasonable , \"","depth":14},{"id":124,"text":"Mr. Rubio said on ABC ' s \" This Week . \"","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Sen. Chris Coons , Delaware Democrat , said","depth":7},{"id":126,"text":"even offering North Korea a summit with the U.S. president is a significant concession ,","depth":7},{"id":127,"text":"while also saying","depth":8},{"id":128,"text":"it ' s important that North Korea has freed several Americans","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"the country was holding as a confidence-building measure .","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"\" But let ' s be clear","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"twice before North Korea under Kim Jong-un ' s father committed to full denuclearization in six party talks in 2005 , in 2007 ...","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"only to then change their tune , \"","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"Mr. Coons said on \" Fox News Sunday . \"","depth":10},{"id":135,"text":"\" So we ' re going to have to be very focused , very engaged , \"","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"Mr. Coons said .","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"\" I am hopeful","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"that Secretary [ of State Mike ] Pompeo will brief and engage Congress .","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"And I ' m hopeful","depth":12},{"id":140,"text":"that we ' ll work together","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"to make sure","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"that this summit is a success . \"","depth":14},{"id":143,"text":"Even Mr. Trump ' s critics have credited the president for his negotiating skills in his recent dealings with Mr. Kim ,","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"and calling the summit a positive step .","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"\" In some ways , Kim Jong-un may have met his match here with our very unconventional president , \"","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"said former Director of National Intelligence James Clapper on CNN ' s \" State of the Union . \"","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"Mr. Clapper ,","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"who ' s publicly butted heads with Mr. Trump over issues","depth":16},{"id":149,"text":"related to Russian interference in the 2016 U.S. election and special counsel Robert Mueller ' s probe ,","depth":16},{"id":150,"text":"said","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"a summit would be good","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"regardless of whether there is any sort of agreement .","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"\" Having gone this far ,","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"there is value in meeting","depth":14},{"id":155,"text":"and greeting ,","depth":14},{"id":156,"text":"gripping","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"and grinning ,","depth":15},{"id":158,"text":"and just establishing a rapport , \"","depth":15},{"id":159,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":160,"text":"\" Yes - I think","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"it would be important to have the summit . \"","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"- This article was based in part on wire service reports .","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":325,"left":324,"right":162,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":324,"left":184,"right":323,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":184,"lef